Date:   Fri Jun 8 15:03:22 2012 +0100

    interval: Add initial and final properties
    
    This allows creating a ClutterInterval from language bindings without
    using the setter functions.

 clutter/clutter-interval.c | 92 ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++----------
