Date:   Thu Apr 19 16:35:39 2012 +0100

    actor: Remove automatic transition init from add_transition()
    
    Adding an explicit transition overrides any consideration of the easing
    state of an actor.

 clutter/clutter-actor.c                      | 11 -----------
